Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.17,0:01:57.63,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but they suddenly asked me to help out at the store, so I can't go.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.63,0:01:59.18,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,Go on ahead by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.84,0:02:01.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takahashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.68,0:02:02.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.47,0:02:04.64,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,Wanna go somewhere today?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.01,0:00:39.89,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Usotsuki na anata nakimushi no atashi
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.89,0:00:45.85,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Doushite umaku ikanai wa
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.85,0:00:51.98,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Oshare shita kami mo rain suton no tsume mo
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.98,0:00:57.95,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Anata wa kidzuki mo shinai ne
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.95,0:01:05.33,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Love kanashii namida nanka ja nai yo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.33,0:01:10.04,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Me ga kawaite hirihiri suru dake
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.04,0:01:15.97,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Kono unmei bakari I love
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.89,0:01:24.85,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Kimi dake wo atashi dake wo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.85,0:01:29.77,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Atsui omoi wo uketomete
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.98,0:01:36.90,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Doko made mo tsunagattetai
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.90,0:01:43.66,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Kawaikunai nakigao mo se mo aishiteru
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.01,0:00:39.89,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Why can't things go well between
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.89,0:00:45.85,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,the liar, you, and the crybaby, me?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.85,0:00:51.98,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't notice my styled hair
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.98,0:00:57.95,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,or my nice set of press-on nails.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.95,0:01:05.33,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Love isn't about the unhappy tears that go along with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.33,0:01:10.04,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Those tears only leave my eyes dry and hurt me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.04,0:01:15.97,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,I love this destiny
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.89,0:01:24.85,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,between only you and only me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.85,0:01:29.77,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to accept your hot feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.98,0:01:36.90,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,and be taken by you forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.90,0:01:43.66,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Despite your uncute, tearful face and your shortness, I still love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.60,0:02:09.02,Episode title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(800,800)\fscx97.5\fscy100\pos(142,384)}Episode 7...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.64,0:02:09.56,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Umm... I was going to an all-you-can-eat cake buffet with Mizu-chin and Taka-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.31,0:02:13.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.94,0:02:21.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's broke whenever she's with me, and she hates having me pay for her, so she only asks for fruit milk...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.74,0:02:22.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.45,0:02:24.62,test,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\fscx157.5\fscy183.75\frz291.907\c&H875ED4&\pos(489,196)}Mizu-chin
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.54,0:02:28.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Weren't you guys going to an all-you-can-eat cake place or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.08,0:02:29.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All-you-can-eat cake?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.62,0:02:31.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, yeah, we went last week.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.54,0:02:34.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nana couldn't go, because she didn't have any money or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.17,0:02:36.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She was pretty green with envy, so why don't you go with her sometime?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.09,0:02:45.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano, where are you headed? I couldn't get Takeuchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.14,0:02:46.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.22,0:02:49.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.98,0:02:51.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you tell?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.31,0:02:52.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in the middle of...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.02,0:02:54.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...stalking my girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.53,0:02:58.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? For a Christmas present?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.32,0:03:03.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I thought you'd know what Yano likes, Takeuchi-kun, so I was hoping we could go shopping for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.95,0:03:08.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure he'd be happy with anything you picked out yourself, Takahashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.04,0:03:09.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.33,0:03:10.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.34,0:03:18.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takeuchi-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.21,0:03:20.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? You can't make it? Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.84,0:03:26.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I really think Yano will like something you pick out yourself a lot more.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.60,0:03:29.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I have no sense for those things...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.27,0:03:32.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Think about it this way. If Yano got you a present...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.35,0:03:36.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...would you prefer something your friends picked out for him that they knew you'd like...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.98,0:03:40.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...or something you don't really like that he picked out himself after lots of consideration?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.86,0:03:42.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which would make you happier?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.95,0:03:43.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.45,0:03:49.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, the one that Yano picked out himself...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.95,0:03:50.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.08,0:03:53.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's on the move again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.63,0:04:02.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, she slipped.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.13,0:04:04.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's she doing, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.26,0:04:05.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I could ask you the same question.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.26,0:04:12.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? She must be out buying you a present.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.65,0:04:20.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though you're penniless...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.36,0:04:23.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You big dummy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.70,0:04:27.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what's going on with Takeuchi?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.16,0:04:30.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, he said he had to help out at the store, so he couldn't come.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.29,0:04:32.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the end of the year, so it makes sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.00,0:04:33.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.12,0:04:36.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just overreacting.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.71,0:04:38.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, here she comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.42,0:04:39.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And she has a bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.21,0:04:40.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.96,0:04:43.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That ends today's stalking!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.63,0:04:48.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-Idiot! She'll notice us!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.14,0:04:51.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you couldn't make it...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.89,0:04:54.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was worried that you might not've been able to get anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.94,0:04:56.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I see you did. I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.48,0:04:59.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was it. See you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.77,0:05:01.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! Since you're out this way, wanna get something to drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.69,0:05:04.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, it's okay. That's really all I came for.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.58,0:05:15.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so tiny...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.37,0:05:17.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard from Masa...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.58,0:05:21.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That girl who was in the accident last year... she was your girlfriend at that time?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.09,0:05:25.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I also heard that you haven't even visited her grave yet, either?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.30,0:05:27.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't do stuff like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.72,0:05:28.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.43,0:05:31.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not saying this for your girlfriend's benefit. I'm saying this for yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.64,0:05:37.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go buy some flowers she liked, some water, and get out there, Motoharu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.14,0:05:38.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People need to cry every now and then--
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.56,0:05:39.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to hear it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.48,0:05:41.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She was a stupid bitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.98,0:05:42.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Moto!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.65,0:05:44.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even stupid bitches feel regret.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.61,0:05:48.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if she does regret it, it's too late!
