Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.45,0:05:55.45,tab.,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx78.75\fscy83.75\frz13.848\pos(410,191)\frx16\fry346\c&HDADDD3&}Clean-up\N Snow shoveling
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.45,0:05:55.45,tab.,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx178.75\fscy98.75\pos(548,200)\frx16\fry0\frz272.81\c&HB6B6B4&}December 24
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.45,0:05:56.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, boys! Take this seriously!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.46,0:05:58.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't have a snowball fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.46,0:05:59.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.38,0:06:01.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez! We'll never finish like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.46,0:06:06.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano hasn't looked at me once today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.97,0:06:08.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it just my imagination?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.97,0:06:15.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It... isn't my imagination!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.98,0:06:17.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.23,0:06:19.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.31,0:06:20.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's he so mad about?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.98,0:06:21.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.45,0:06:30.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takahashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.87,0:06:34.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, that's stupid. Get up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.08,0:06:36.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takahashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.48,0:07:05.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.90,0:07:12.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't screw around like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.54,0:07:19.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was obviously a joke...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.41,0:07:22.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.83,0:07:27.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I still might not have fully understood Yano at that time...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.55,0:07:28.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.72,0:07:31.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.44,0:07:50.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's your Christmas present, you bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.51,0:08:15.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.89,0:08:18.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't do it out of spite...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.81,0:08:22.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay. Because you're still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.31,0:08:28.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It can be really painful at times...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.23,0:08:31.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.74,0:08:34.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm, I had a really hard time deciding.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.91,0:08:36.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, it's a cap.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.74,0:08:38.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.16,0:08:42.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said you liked hats, and I didn't think you had one with a fuzzy ball on top...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.75,0:08:44.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I had a really hard time picking the colors...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.83,0:08:47.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but if you don't like it, they said you could come back and exchange it for another!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.71,0:08:49.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would I?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.75,0:08:52.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think it suits me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.80,0:08:57.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It does!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.76,0:08:58.60,test,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\c&H774EE9&\b1\frz90\fscx325\fscy317.5\pos(62,300)}Incredibly...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.72,0:08:58.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.30,0:09:00.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.35,0:09:03.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's mine, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.57,0:09:14.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I'll be drinking nothing but fruit milk for a while myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.58,0:09:20.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're crying? Doofus.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.95,0:09:22.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just that...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.33,0:09:24.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything and anything moves you, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.71,0:09:25.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.54,0:09:29.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People are always telling me to only cry when I'm sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.30,0:09:36.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you have to cry, then I think tears of happiness are a lot better than tears of sadness.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.59,0:09:45.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since I met Yano, I've felt that my tears have gotten so much more fragile.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.98,0:09:51.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! I left my Math book in my locker!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.32,0:09:53.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Let's go back and get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.40,0:09:54.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's such a pain...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.57,0:09:57.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say that. We were assigned a ton of homework.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.61,0:10:00.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I'm going to the girl's room  for a second, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.78,0:10:01.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.17,0:10:16.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For when I fell down the stairs the other day...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.55,0:10:17.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.55,0:10:18.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.97,0:10:21.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But don't save me ever again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.14,0:10:23.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to owe you anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.52,0:10:29.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you hate me that much, we shouldn't have even gotten to know each other to begin with.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.61,0:10:35.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You only used me to get revenge on my sister, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.70,0:10:38.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Revenge"?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.49,0:10:41.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That wouldn't mean anything, and I'd have no reason to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.57,0:10:43.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go giving everything a hidden meaning.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.75,0:10:50.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, why did you cry back then?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.46,0:10:54.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you cry that time?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.98,0:11:13.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.70,0:11:20.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Cry"?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.99,0:11:22.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano cried?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.61,0:11:25.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Has something like that ever really happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.49,0:11:28.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, why did you cry back then?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.41,0:11:31.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When did this happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.50,0:11:34.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And in front of Yamamoto-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.84,0:11:37.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What could make that happen...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.09,0:11:46.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for making you listen to my problems again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.10,0:11:48.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And we're on winter break, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.02,0:11:51.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay. I was wondering what was up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.39,0:11:55.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking honestly for a sec, I... can't really believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.69,0:11:57.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That he actually cried.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.11,0:12:04.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've known him almost my whole life, but I've never seen him cry or show his soft side.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.11,0:12:07.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you told me that before, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.12,0:12:08.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess it's because he's human.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.87,0:12:13.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone can always do that when nobody else is around...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.12,0:12:17.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but I always thought Yano was different.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.63,0:12:21.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can understand, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.63,0:12:23.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.72,0:12:30.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm... did something happen between Yamamoto-san and Yano in middle school?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.06,0:12:33.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sometimes, I think there's something strange between them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.98,0:12:37.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not really. Nothing unusual, at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.06,0:12:38.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yamamoto was like that back then, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.90,0:12:41.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If they seem kind of awkward to you, then isn't it just because...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.65,0:12:44.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...they're both related to Nana-san in some way?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.57,0:12:51.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder why Nana-san was in that car with her ex...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.50,0:12:55.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder why she did something like that to betray Yano...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.79,0:12:58.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was her ex really that charming?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.84,0:13:00.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.50,0:13:02.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was the worst.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.30,0:13:05.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone was always asking why she was going out with a bum like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.88,0:13:07.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She was always bruised all over.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.80,0:13:09.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bruised?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.47,0:13:11.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would she stay with someone like him?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.02,0:13:15.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People also always asked Yano, "Why are you with someone as stupid as that?"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.15,0:13:20.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's just what love is.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.78,0:13:23.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.07,0:13:26.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's something only those in the relationship could know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.20,0:13:28.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.16,0:13:31.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for calling you out when it's so cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.49,0:13:34.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano and I must really seem like such a stupid couple, too, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.16,0:13:36.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Getting everyone involved like this and working ourselves up over every little thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.29,0:13:41.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all. I think any couple that isn't stupid isn't a real couple anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.26,0:13:46.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takeuchi-kun, when those two first started going out...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.97,0:13:50.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...did you also think "why was he going out with someone so stupid?"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.39,0:13:52.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.06,0:13:58.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It pissed me off... they were so dumb and stupid that I couldn't take my eyes off them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.40,0:13:59.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since the beginning.
