Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.75,0:14:16.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in the front again!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.58,0:14:18.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no luck with getting seats!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.58,0:14:20.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, look.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.30,0:14:24.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.84,0:14:27.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Talk about the worst possible combination.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.84,0:14:30.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That seating change was the worst.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.84,0:14:33.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't be able to leave anything behind now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.26,0:14:35.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, when you forget your textbook, you can ask me for mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.89,0:14:37.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The person next to me will let me share.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.89,0:14:41.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks. And when I start nodding off and it seems like I'm gonna be called on, poke me, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.40,0:14:42.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a little impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.69,0:14:45.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... this will be the second time I'll be sitting next to Yamamoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.23,0:14:47.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The second time since my second year of middle school.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.49,0:14:51.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? She didn't share her textbooks then, either?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.07,0:14:56.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, yeah. Or... maybe not. I don't think I ever forgot them back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.04,0:14:58.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.75,0:15:03.88,test,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(270,0)\fscx205\fscy215\pos(92,347)\c&HE3E3E3&}What happened\N between you and\N Yamamoto-san\N during middle\N school?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.88,0:15:06.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.63,0:15:12.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm no good. When I think Nana-san's involved, I can't help getting weak in the knees.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.55,0:15:16.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, when you went to get my present did you try to buy it with Takeuchi?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.52,0:15:17.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.22,0:15:19.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you lie and say you were going to an all-you-can-eat cake buffet with Mizu-chin?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.10,0:15:24.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lie...? I just wanted to surprise you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.48,0:15:25.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.98,0:15:26.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.94,0:15:29.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't lie to me if you're going to be meeting with another guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.95,0:15:32.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want any secrets between us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.33,0:15:36.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Promise me that you'll never ever betray me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.62,0:15:38.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.21,0:15:45.17,test,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx261.25\fscy212.5\pos(534,218)\frx12\fry0\frz322.354}English
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.13,0:15:47.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What page are we working on today?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.80,0:15:49.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me see!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.84,0:15:53.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it kinda harsh to be sitting next to Yamamoto-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.84,0:15:57.85,note,,0000,0000,0000,,Asahi Middle School
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.80,0:15:55.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She doesn't say anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.89,0:15:57.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She scowled at me the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.81,0:16:00.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's kinda hard to ask her to see her textbook, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.39,0:16:02.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope they change seats soon.
