Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.89,0:16:04.69,tab.,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(188,235)\fscx82.5\fscy107.5\c&HF3F4ED&}Fujii
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.89,0:16:04.69,tab.,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx82.5\fscy100\pos(273,226)\c&HF3F4ED&}Mitsuhashi
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.89,0:16:04.69,tab.,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(177,355)\fscx120\fscy111.25\c&HF3F4ED&}Yano
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.89,0:16:04.69,tab.,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx86.25\fscy100\pos(282,350)\c&HF3F4ED&}Yamamoto
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.89,0:16:04.69,tab.,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx141.25\fscy160\pos(481,379)\c&HF3F4ED&}Seat Changes
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.65,0:16:06.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me see your textbook.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.23,0:16:10.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hard to see from here, so could you put it between our desks?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.57,0:16:16.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Open to page 45.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.95,0:16:18.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.13,0:16:26.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you working ten pages ahead?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.13,0:16:30.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing else to do at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.38,0:16:32.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing else to do, so you study?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.68,0:16:36.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure are different.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.43,0:16:39.93,tab.,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HF3F4ED&\fscx161.25\fscy157.5\pos(300,193)\frz9.717\frx18\fry336}Study hall!!\N Keep quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.59,0:17:17.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd sure like some money right about now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.55,0:17:20.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't talk about your unrealistic dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.39,0:17:21.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have dreams!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.47,0:17:24.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I were rich, we could go on a date at Disney Land!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.60,0:17:27.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about you, Yano? What would you do if you were rich?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.19,0:17:28.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.15,0:17:29.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need money.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.90,0:17:33.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need any money, but instead... I want love.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.28,0:17:39.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with me, wishing to be rich?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.66,0:17:43.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano, don't worry! I'll give you as much love as you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.29,0:17:43.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.87,0:17:44.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.96,0:17:46.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, why don't you come over on Saturday? My parents won't be around.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.63,0:17:51.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So love meant the perverted stuff to Yano...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.29,0:17:53.87,test,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\an8\c&HB06374&\fscx273.75\fscy213.75\b1}Sign: Slurp
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.01,0:17:57.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano... in that case, want to come over my place on Saturday?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.22,0:17:58.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Your parents won't be around?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.76,0:17:59.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They will.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.68,0:18:00.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then that's no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.64,0:18:03.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.93,0:18:04.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.68,0:18:07.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that all you think about?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.73,0:18:08.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.23,0:18:11.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're such a moron.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.15,0:18:16.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Yano. I can't live up to your expectations.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.03,0:18:19.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My heart hurts, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.07,0:18:20.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, check it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.16,0:18:21.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They look just like you, Takahashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.41,0:18:23.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Should I give it a whirl?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.37,0:18:25.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? I thought you were broke.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.29,0:18:26.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my entire life's savings.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.62,0:18:29.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.46,0:18:31.21,overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as Yano smiles back at me, that's all I need.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.00,0:18:31.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, that yellow one is cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.21,0:18:34.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I should just put my other worries to rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.97,0:18:45.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want Yano... to always smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.85,0:18:50.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? I don't have my biology textbook.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.40,0:18:53.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I somehow managed to bring it home, I guess I forgot to bring it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.44,0:18:55.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're such a doofus. Want to borrow mine?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.23,0:18:57.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.77,0:18:59.69,test,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx138.75\fscy107.5\pos(329,359)\frx10\fry0\frz182.742\c&H738190&}Biology
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.24,0:19:02.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.45,0:19:03.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On second thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.99,0:19:07.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me see yours, Yamamoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.05,0:19:15.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.39,0:19:26.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.43,0:19:28.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-Nothing! B-Bye bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.85,0:19:33.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do I want...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.44,0:19:36.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yamamoto-san sure was nice, showing you her textbook.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.94,0:19:38.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.90,0:19:42.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano, wanna come to my house on Sunday?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.32,0:19:45.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It should be convenient for you, since it's Sunday.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.03,0:19:46.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are your parents going to be out or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.99,0:19:48.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.12,0:19:53.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.54,0:19:56.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.55,0:19:58.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's kinda cramped in here, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.51,0:20:00.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You... knew from the very beginning, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.21,0:20:03.13,test,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\b1\fscx196.25\fscy161.25\pos(208,31)\c&HBC4526&}Whatever are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.09,0:20:05.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's smaller than your room, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.55,0:20:08.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh. You can put your bag down over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.14,0:20:10.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano's in my room!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.64,0:20:13.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm... a little moved by it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.19,0:20:18.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.36,0:20:19.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.07,0:20:20.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, where do you live?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.99,0:20:22.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yanagimachi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.07,0:20:24.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It must've taken you a while to get here, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.16,0:20:26.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all. I just have to take one bus.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.74,0:20:27.20,overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom and Yano are talking...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.20,0:20:28.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so handsome. Your class must really talk about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.20,0:20:29.37,overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,It feels so weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.24,0:20:29.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, no... not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.24,0:20:31.65,test,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord3\c&H705CE9&\3c&H61EDF4&\b1\fscx225\fscy171.25\move(647,37,-44,37,0,2399)}Mother in the middle of appraisal
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.58,0:20:35.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, geez... I'm starting to feel bad for Yano.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.33,0:20:35.46,overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,What does your father do for a living?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.46,0:20:39.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, he's involved with realty. Umm, Yano's house is really huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.84,0:20:43.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? And just when did you pay them a visit?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.18,0:20:45.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.18,0:20:48.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takahashi, that house isn't as big as you think it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.72,0:20:52.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've never come in, but my room is only four and a half tatami mats.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.77,0:20:55.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Oh? Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.81,0:20:57.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My. I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.07,0:21:03.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Should I play a CD? What do you wanna listen to?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.11,0:21:05.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anything's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.07,0:21:10.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it... it's totally different from meeting with him outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.37,0:21:11.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so nervous!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.58,0:21:14.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone save me from this silence!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.54,0:21:18.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not gonna do anything, so calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.42,0:21:21.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, it seems like your mom would just walk in without knocking.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.80,0:21:23.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-How rude!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.17,0:21:24.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She wouldn't do anything like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.09,0:21:27.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please have some more tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.72,0:21:32.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.27,0:21:33.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For what?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.77,0:21:34.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A lot of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.77,0:21:37.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it. You're just being treated preciously.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.61,0:21:45.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano, I really, really love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.86,0:21:50.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like I've learned so much more about you since we started dating!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.04,0:21:52.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.41,0:21:55.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like? Like...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.16,0:21:58.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can be a bigger doofus than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.04,0:22:02.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like your more childish aspects...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.84,0:22:06.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And how you brush my hair like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.18,0:22:08.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just keep falling more and more in love with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.18,0:22:14.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm jealous of Yamamoto-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.73,0:22:18.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of Yamamoto-san, who knows more about the unknown Yano than me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.15,0:22:20.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to be the closest one to Yano.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.69,0:22:22.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to know more and more about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.19,0:22:24.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to know everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.44,0:22:28.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it selfish of me to want that? I wonder...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.99,0:22:31.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano, umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.54,0:22:36.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said before that there'd be no secrets between us, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.41,0:22:37.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.46,0:22:40.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never lie to you ever again.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.25,0:22:42.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So don't lie to me either, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.54,0:22:44.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.05,0:22:46.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.34,0:22:49.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure it's all just in my head...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.55,0:22:52.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...what happened between you and Yamamoto-san in middle school?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.56,0:22:56.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.94,0:23:00.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.02,0:23:02.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why what?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.02,0:23:03.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For the same reason you have.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.77,0:23:05.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's making me uneasy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.07,0:23:11.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There aren't going to be any secrets between us, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.20,0:23:12.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.74,0:23:16.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.21,0:23:25.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why won't you answer me?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.52,0:23:43.94,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Kisetsu ga sukoshi ugoita ki ga suru
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.94,0:23:52.41,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Hizashi mo mijikaku itsukazurete
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.41,0:24:00.83,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Futari no basu ha kawaranai machi
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.83,0:24:08.09,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Hashitteiru koto hotto shiteta
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.09,0:24:16.97,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Mado no soto itsumo mitai ni miteru anata
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.97,0:24:25.40,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Soshite watashi mo mane wo shiteiru
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.40,0:24:29.24,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,itsumo mitai ni
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.24,0:24:37.74,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Nee futari ha onaji nano ka na?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.74,0:24:45.75,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Ikitai basho ha? Damatteitatte iinda yo ne?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.75,0:24:54.59,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Nee futari ha onaji nano ka na?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.59,0:25:04.15,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Itoshii kimochi... Anata no shisen ha ima, mienakute....
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.52,0:23:43.94,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like the seasons have changed slightly
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.94,0:23:52.41,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,and the sunbeams have thinned and will one day shift.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.41,0:24:00.83,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,But I was relieved, knowing our bus
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.83,0:24:08.09,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,was riding through our unchanged city.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.09,0:24:16.97,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,You always gaze up to me from outside my window
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.97,0:24:25.40,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,and I mimic you by doing the same
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.40,0:24:29.24,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,like always.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.24,0:24:37.74,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I wonder if we're both the same?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.74,0:24:45.75,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if the place we want to go to has gotten dull, it's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.75,0:24:54.59,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I wonder if we're both the same?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.59,0:25:04.15,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,I still feel love for you, but you're no longer looking at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.96,0:25:34.98,Episode title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\3c&HDC6CE3&\c&HFDE2FF&\fscx97.5\fscy122.5\pos(450,377)}Episode 8 Preview...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.44,0:25:09.53,after ending,,0000,0000,0000,,Yamamoto-san loved you?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.11,0:25:13.61,after ending,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care whether\N Yamamoto loved or hated me.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.61,0:25:15.70,after ending,,0000,0000,0000,,It has nothing to do with me.\N Not interested one bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.12,0:25:20.20,after ending,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw you two go\N home together that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.20,0:25:22.37,after ending,,0000,0000,0000,,How could you do\N it with her little sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.71,0:25:26.00,after ending,,0000,0000,0000,,Come with me, Takahashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.00,0:25:27.79,after ending,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine with me...
